songs.title: Return To Aztlán
songs.lyrics:
Tianguistengo chicomostoc
Teotihuacan cancun
Cocula taxco tecojote
Comixtle zacapoaxtla

Sei Agotzingo
Home nenepil
Chei tepetate
Anahui chinicuil

Acuini, chipoxtli, chicomi, chihuei
Acuini, chipoxtli, chicomi, chihuei

Iztlixochitl reina xochitl
Moctezuma ra ra ra
Tlachiquero chiquihuite
Chilpayate chupirul

Iztlixochitl reina xochitl
Moctezuma ra ra ra
Chocolate molcajete
Cacahuate Cha cha cha

Huitlacoche tlachicoton
Chipotle metepec
Chimalpopocan zacoaltipan
Mecapales tezozomoc

Sei Achichintle
Home Huacarock
Chei tepesquite
Anahui jalostoc

Acuini, chipoxtli, chicomi, chihuei
Acuini, chipoxtli, chicomi, chihuei

Polzolcalli Rockotitlan
Cacaxtla zacatlan
Mecate esquite chirimoya
Chichimeca machu pichu

Sei Chilpayate
Home Nahualon
Chei tepalcate
Anahui Chano y chon

Acuini, chipoxtli, chicomi, chihuei
Acuini, chipoxtli, chicomi, chihuei

Iztlixochitl reina xochitl
Moctezuma ra ra ra
Tlachiquero chiquihuite
Chilpayate chupirul

Iztlixochitl reina xochitl
Moctezuma ra ra ra
Chocolate molcajete
Cacahuate Cha cha cha
